VOTER Protocol — Third-Party Software Inventory
================================================

This file catalogs third-party software bundled in or distributed alongside
this repository. It exists to satisfy Apache License 2.0 §4(d) attribution
requirements for downstream consumers (Etherscan-equivalents, SBOM
scanners, npm consumers) and to provide a single auditable point of
reference for license obligations.

For copyright statements and a short narrative, see NOTICE.
For the upstream licenses themselves, follow the links and paths below.

Each entry is structured as:
  Project  — License  — Copyright holder
    Bundled at: <path or package name>
    Why bundled: <reason>

