Verification notes
------------------

This inventory was generated from a direct survey of:
  - .gitmodules (git submodule registration)
  - contracts/lib/ (vendored Solidity libraries)
  - packages/*/package.json (declared npm dependencies)
  - File-level SPDX headers on .sol files in contracts/src/verifiers/
    and packages/crypto/contracts/verifiers/

If new third-party code is bundled (e.g., solmate, openzeppelin-contracts-
upgradeable, additional Aztec circuits), an entry must be added here
before the change is merged. See CONTRIBUTING.md for the dependency-
addition checklist.

Upstream NOTICE-file propagation
--------------------------------

At the time of writing, the installed `@aztec/bb.js` package and the
`@noir-lang/*` packages do not ship a NOTICE file with their distributed
artifacts. If a future upstream release introduces a NOTICE file, its
content must be appended here and to NOTICE per Apache License 2.0 §4(d).

